belief of your own volition.

13
00:01:31,890 --> 00:01:34,320
Yes.

14
00:01:38,380 --> 00:01:44,270
But I'm feeling a bit sad. Hui Yeong.

15
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:51,220
Be well, and don't lose contact.

16
00:01:52,300 --> 00:01:55,070
I will do that.

17
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:31,950
Soo Bin.

18
00:02:36,820 --> 00:02:39,340
You're going to be all right?

19
00:02:40,630 --> 00:02:43,000
I will be.

20
00:02:46,190 --> 00:02:49,140
Bye.

21
00:03:03,210 --> 00:03:07,120
You said that me dropping out was running away.

22
00:03:07,830 --> 00:03:11,660
So I thought a lot about it.

23
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:18,460
This is the only path I can see right now.

24
00:03:19,500 --> 00:03:26,750
Studying hard and attending school
with kids who have been going to school with sincerity

25
00:03:27,980 --> 00:03:30,780
makes me feel too guilty.

26
00:03:37,330 --> 00:03:41,910
The things I did to you, I'll pay for them all

27
00:03:41,910 --> 00:03:44,750
and live while repenting.

28
00:03:45,470 --> 00:03:47,590
Joon Woo.

29
00:03:50,790 --> 00:03:54,050
Thank you for forgiving me.

30
