Shelter Psychiatric Convalescent Hospital

93
00:10:04,090 --> 00:10:07,820
Hyung, have you been well?

94
00:10:07,820 --> 00:10:15,120
Mom and Dad have been busy, so I came.
They're doing well.

95
00:10:17,940 --> 00:10:21,760
And I dropped out of school.

96
00:10:21,760 --> 00:10:24,910
I wanted time to think...

97
00:10:27,150 --> 00:10:30,580
how I should live.

98
00:10:48,530 --> 00:10:51,600
You know what?

99
00:10:53,020 --> 00:10:56,930
Since we were little, you were my role model.

100
00:11:01,650 --> 00:11:05,740
You were smart and you were good in school.

101
00:11:05,740 --> 00:11:10,620
Good in sports and good-looking.

102
00:11:12,880 --> 00:11:16,420
Mom and Dad liked you the best.

103
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:20,690
And they were the proudest of you.

104
00:11:23,300 --> 00:11:27,280
They always told me to do just as much as you.

105
00:11:28,510 --> 00:11:31,270
Just as much as you...

106
00:11:37,100 --> 00:11:40,970
But I'm not going to make that effort anymore.

107
00:11:40,970 --> 00:11:44,280
I'm just going to do as much as it suits me.

108
00:11:45,770 --> 00:11:48,850
As much as I can do.

109
00:11:51,340 --> 00:11:54,120
I'm going to find out for myself...

110
00:11:55,020 --> 00:11:58,230
what I have to do.

111
00:12:00,990 --> 00:12:04,030
Someone told me.

112
00:12:37,430 --> 00:12:40,880
I wonder if Joon Woo's doing well.

113
00:12:45,630 --> 00:12:51,020
- Soo Bin.
- Mom!
- Come.

114
00:12:51,020 --> 00:12:54,720
It's been a long time since we've been on a date.

115
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:57,460
Sorry. I've been so busy.

116
00:12:57,460 --> 00:13:01,020
It's okay. I think how you work is cool.

117
00:13:02,210 --> 00:13:06,950
Soo Bin, I thought about it,

118
00:13:08,530 --> 00:13:15,350
and from now on, I'll make an effort to trust you more.

119
00:13:15,350 --> 00:13:22,330
But, right now, I can't cheer your relationship on.

120
00:13:22,330 --> 00:13:29,830
- I know.
- But sorry for reacting so emotionally to it before.

121
00:13:31,430 --> 00:13:37,530
Mom.
Can I make a request?

122
00:13:37,530 --> 00:13:39,790
What is it?

123
00:13:40,630 --> 00:13:46,740
I would like you to... not mind Dad and

124
00:13:46,740 --> 00:13:50,670
just live well courageously.

125
00:13:50,670 --> 00:13:54,600
Until now, you've made your best effort.

126
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:58,640
So don't think about what others think.

127
00:13:59,430 --> 00:14:03,560
If it's because of me, I'm really fine.

128
00:14:04,400 --> 00:14:08,010
As you've done until now,

129
00:14:08,010 --> 00:14:12,980
I'd like you to live resolutely, cooly.

130
00:14:12,980 --> 00:14:17,810
Not as Yoo Soo Bin's mom or Yoo Joong Soo's wife

131
00:14:18,620 --> 00:14:23,750
but as a cool career woman, Yoon Song Hee,
just as you are.

132
00:14:27,820 --> 00:14:30,110
Huh?

133
00:14:30,110 --> 00:14:34,910
Soo Bin, would we be able to order more
after finishing all this?

134
00:14:34,910 --> 00:14:38,650
More than this?

135
00:14:54,930 --> 00:14:57,330
- Yeah, Mom.
- Oh, Joon Woo, did you do well?

136
00:14:57,330 --> 00:15:01,600
I tried my best, but I'm not sure.
Other kids are good.

137
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:06,910
But I'm sure you did the best.
Good job, my son.

138
00:15:06,910 --> 00:15:10,750
But where are you?
Why is there an echo?

139
00:15:10,750 --> 00:15:16,840
Oh, I came to a big market.
I ran out of ingredients.

140
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:20,880
I see. Mom,

141
00:15:20,880 --> 00:15:24,370
- should I come by today?
- Huh?

142
00:15:25,290 --> 00:15:27,480
Why are you so shocked?

143
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:32,070
You have to get home and get some rest.
Why would you come here?

144
00:15:32,070 --> 00:15:35,540
I got it. Eat well.

145
00:15:35,540 --> 00:15:40,350
Okay. You, too. Bye.

146
00:15:41,760 --> 00:15:45,590
- But there's Aunt Hye Yeong.
- She's not feeling well these days.

147
00:15:45,590 --> 00:15:48,330
You don't look well either.
Are you sick?

148
00:15:48,330 --> 00:15:53,240
No, I'm totally well.

149
00:16:27,240 --> 00:16:29,550
Soo Bin.

150
00:16:31,270 --> 00:16:35,270
I'm with my mom.
Should we text?

151
00:16:37,040 --> 00:16:39,930
Soo Bin, I did well.

152
00:16:39,930 --> 00:16:42,780
You worked hard.
Are you going home?

153
00:16:42,780 --> 00:16:46,450
No. To my mom.
To surprise her.

154
00:16:46,450 --> 00:16:49,850
Oh, she'll be happy.
Get back safe.

155
00:16:49,850 --> 00:16:53,690
I had a date with my mom.

156
00:18:08,090 --> 00:18:11,840
Yeah, Mom.
Did you get home okay?

157
00:18:11,840 --> 00:18:16,590
Yeah.
I just closed up, and now I'm cleaning up.

158
00:18:17,870 --> 00:18:22,270
How is business?
It's going well?

159
00:18:22,270 --> 00:18:25,800
Yeah. Yeah, of course.

160
00:18:27,700 --> 00:18:30,260
Okay.

161
00:18:45,750 --> 00:18:48,630
Aunt Hye Yeong

162
00:18:48,630 --> 00:18:54,490
The phone has been turned off,
so the call cannot be connected.

163
00:19:04,690 --> 00:19:09,670
Aunt, it's me, Joon Woo.

164
00:19:12,600 --> 00:19:16,970
Have you been well?
By chance,

165
00:19:18,510 --> 00:19:23,280
did something happen to Mom's eatery?

166
00:19:29,240 --> 00:19:31,980
Tell me.

167
00:19:41,430 --> 00:19:43,970
Yes.

168
00:20:07,640 --> 00:20:12,690
Joon Woo, are you sleeping?
Did you get back okay?

169
00:20:13,450 --> 00:20:17,470
Yeah, I did.

170
00:20:17,470 --> 00:20:20,360
Can I call you?

171
00:20:46,910 --> 00:20:51,460
Joon Woo,
your mom was happy you surprised her, right?

172
00:20:51,460 --> 00:20:53,660
Yeah.

173
00:20:57,420 --> 00:21:03,140
But it feels like you're worried about something.

174
00:21:03,140 --> 00:21:05,680
I'm not.

175
00:21:05,680 --> 00:21:11,650
No, I could tell through your texts.

176
00:21:12,910 --> 00:21:18,930
No. Maybe it's because I was a little nervous today.

177
00:21:18,930 --> 00:21:24,010
I see.
You must be tired today.

178
00:21:24,010 --> 00:21:27,680
Yeah. Today, I am a little.

179
00:21:27,680 --> 00:21:33,280
Then I'll sing you a lullaby so you can get good sleep.

180
00:21:34,410 --> 00:21:36,600
Yeah.

181
00:22:06,680 --> 00:22:09,170
Oh, Joon Woo's mom!
Hurry up and get in!

182
00:22:09,170 --> 00:22:11,640
- Sorry for being late!
- Why are you late?

183
00:22:11,640 --> 00:22:14,070
Sorry.

184
00:22:31,050 --> 00:22:35,830
- Don't be late tomorrow.
- Okay. Thank you.

185
00:22:38,230 --> 00:22:41,170
Oh, I'm so sleepy.

186
00:23:29,110 --> 00:23:33,660
- Yeah, Joon Woo.
- Mom, what are you doing?

187
00:23:33,660 --> 00:23:38,050
What do you mean?
I have a lot of customers right now. I'm busy.

188
00:23:38,050 --> 00:23:40,750
You're not.

189
00:24:23,010 --> 00:24:28,190
Mom.
Tell me the truth.

190
00:24:28,190 --> 00:24:32,680
What situation you're in, how bad it is.

191
00:24:33,900 --> 00:24:37,400
Don't worry. I'll figure it out myself.

192
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:40,140
How is this figuring out yourself?

193
00:24:41,230 --> 00:24:46,950
Mom. I'm not a kid anymore.
You have to discuss with me if something's going on.

194
00:24:46,950 --> 00:24:50,490
We're the only family we've got.

195
00:24:50,500 --> 00:24:53,650
I'm your guardian, too.

196
00:24:53,650 --> 00:24:56,700
Why do you keep trying to shoulder
the burden by yourself?

197
00:24:59,270 --> 00:25:04,100
Not knowing the situation until now,
it already makes me feel guilty and taken aback.

198
00:25:04,980 --> 00:25:08,620
Joon Woo, don't be like that.

199
00:25:09,920 --> 00:25:16,860
I only hid things from you out of necessity.
You did nothing wrong.

200
00:25:16,860 --> 00:25:18,670
Mom.

201
00:25:20,920 --> 00:25:26,390
Tell me everything. I want to know.

202
00:25:30,830 --> 00:25:37,580
To be honest, Aunt Hye Yeong took the remodeling money,

203
00:25:37,580 --> 00:25:40,200
but I can't get in touch.

204
00:25:40,200 --> 00:25:46,180
It's a fairly large amount that I overextended myself to give.

205
00:25:48,710 --> 00:25:53,510
Right now, rather than making money
while sustaining the eatery,

206
00:25:53,510 --> 00:25:57,390
working part-time is better.
That's why I did it.

207
00:25:59,170 --> 00:26:02,740
I'll take care of it.
Don't worry, Joon Woo.

208
00:26:02,740 --> 00:26:05,470
I'm going to open up the shop again,

209
00:26:05,470 --> 00:26:12,800
so you just concentrate on your entrance exams. Okay?

210
00:26:12,800 --> 00:26:15,740
Mom...

211
00:26:15,740 --> 00:26:18,650
Sorry.

212
00:26:40,040 --> 00:26:42,880
Monthly spending...

213
00:26:46,050 --> 00:26:50,220
Electricity, food cost...

214
00:26:50,220 --> 00:26:54,400
transportation and academy tuition, too.

215
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:57,230
Total is...

216
00:27:22,800 --> 00:27:26,900
- Joon Woo, what are you doing?
- I'm at the academy.

217
00:27:26,900 --> 00:27:32,300
- You're doing well, right?
- Yeah, I'm doing well.

218
00:27:40,740 --> 00:27:43,470
Good bye.

219
00:28:14,950 --> 00:28:17,220
Should we run away quick?

220
00:28:20,510 --> 00:28:23,820
I was busy yesterday, so I couldn't call.

221
00:28:26,250 --> 00:28:32,710
Joon Woo, do you remember getting rained on here?

222
00:28:35,520 --> 00:28:38,490
Why did you do that then?

223
00:28:38,490 --> 00:28:43,210
Did you think you could block it?

224
00:28:43,210 --> 00:28:45,830
I don't know.

225
00:28:48,140 --> 00:28:53,550
That time, it was a feeling I had for the very first time.

226
00:28:53,550 --> 00:28:56,100
What kind?

227
00:28:58,180 --> 00:29:03,170
By getting completely soaked in the rain with you,

228
00:29:03,170 --> 00:29:07,820
it felt like all my upset feelings were getting washed away.

229
00:29:09,850 --> 00:29:14,780
Joon Woo, what are you doing over the summer break?

230
00:29:17,150 --> 00:29:19,570
Not sure.

231
00:29:22,250 --> 00:29:26,260
Finally, the summer vacation

232
00:29:26,260 --> 00:29:30,100
- is back!
- It's back!

233
00:29:31,430 --> 00:29:35,530
Wow, you guys were nowhere near
excited when I suggested the school trip.

234
00:29:35,530 --> 00:29:37,860
- You're that happy now that you don't have to see me?
- Yes!

235
00:29:37,860 --> 00:29:41,540
- Yoo Pil Sang.
- Not true. I'm sad.

236
00:29:41,540 --> 00:29:44,100
How will I spend the summer without you?

237
00:29:44,100 --> 00:29:48,260
Hey, Pil Sang, stop putting it on a show and check
for your homework for each subject online .

238
00:29:48,260 --> 00:29:52,300
Everyone, have a healthy and full summer break.

239
00:29:52,300 --> 00:29:55,810
And don't call me too often because you miss me!

240
00:29:55,810 --> 00:29:59,460
- Teach, can I follow your Insta?
Follow me back, too!

241
00:29:59,460 --> 00:30:02,540
I was already following you.

242
00:30:02,540 --> 00:30:05,330
Oh.

243
00:30:05,330 --> 00:30:10,650
Oh Han Gyeol,
you did well at being a homeroom teacher for the first time.

244
00:30:10,650 --> 00:30:13,660
You did well.

245
00:30:23,000 --> 00:30:28,800
Now then that's it.
Have a good break. Good bye!

246
00:30:28,800 --> 00:30:32,030
Good bye!

247
00:30:32,030 --> 00:30:33,920
Why is he being like that?
He's so nerdy.

248
00:30:33,920 --> 00:30:36,910
Guys, how about going out to celebrate our break?

249
00:30:36,910 --> 00:30:39,500
When are you going to keep your promise. Please?

250
00:30:39,500 --> 00:30:41,020
I have to ask my mom.

251
00:30:41,020 --> 00:30:45,180
- Come along if you want.
- Oh, then I should. I should.

252
00:30:45,180 --> 00:30:48,100
Jeong Oh Je, Choi Joon Woo, you guys come, too!

