00:30:48,100 --> 00:30:51,870
Pack up your bags.

254
00:30:54,680 --> 00:30:58,700
You're so excited.

255
00:31:01,490 --> 00:31:03,550
Teach!

256
00:31:03,580 --> 00:31:10,090
Excuse me, Ji Min, we're at school.
Please calm down. Be calm.

257
00:31:11,270 --> 00:31:16,040
- I...
- No, it-it's okay if it's a no this time.

258
00:31:16,040 --> 00:31:21,000
Today, should we go shopping?
Or to eat some meat?

259
00:31:21,810 --> 00:31:25,810
I got accepted, Teach!
I got accepted!

260
00:31:25,810 --> 00:31:29,320
Really? Rea—

261
00:31:31,070 --> 00:31:35,140
Ji Min, first, let's leave here.

262
00:31:35,140 --> 00:31:38,990
Wow, Gi Tae, you're working hard
on your in-school volunteer work!

263
00:31:38,990 --> 00:31:41,460
Oh, wait, wait, wait.

264
00:31:41,460 --> 00:31:45,100
- Throw away your own trash.
- Just what I have now.

265
00:31:45,100 --> 00:31:48,340
Anyway, did you see Hui Yeong leave?

266
00:31:48,340 --> 00:31:54,760
I didn't.
He'll probably call when he's sorted out his feelings.

267
00:31:55,910 --> 00:31:58,890
Ah, pick up the trash properly!

268
00:31:58,890 --> 00:32:01,870
Sung Hoon, leave.

269
00:32:04,800 --> 00:32:06,980
Work hard.

270
00:32:16,610 --> 00:32:18,330
Well done!

271
00:32:18,330 --> 00:32:20,150
Yoo Pil Sang, you're not bad at bowling.

272
00:32:20,150 --> 00:32:23,760
Of course, I'm good at everything aside from studying.
I'm good to you, too.

273
00:32:23,760 --> 00:32:27,290
Never mind. Okay, Yoo Pil Sang,
I'll watch the movie with you this Saturday.

274
00:32:27,290 --> 00:32:28,560
Oh, really?

275
00:32:28,560 --> 00:32:33,600
But, with you, you, and you, you, all together.
Otherwise, I won't.

276
00:32:33,600 --> 00:32:36,570
Guys, please help me.
I'll-I'll pay for the movie.

277
00:32:36,570 --> 00:32:41,000
Hey!
You think we don't have the money, Yoo Pil Sang?!

278
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:42,550
Thanks!

279
00:32:43,550 --> 00:32:45,180
Hey, let's go!

280
00:32:45,180 --> 00:32:46,890
Let's do one more round before we go.

281
00:32:58,790 --> 00:33:04,740
Wow, it feels like a dream.
Ji Min got accepted.

282
00:33:07,420 --> 00:33:11,280
She said she's going to the bathroom.
What's taking so long?

283
00:33:14,470 --> 00:33:17,230
What is this, Ji Min?

284
00:33:17,230 --> 00:33:20,260
Teach, thanks for waiting for me.

285
00:33:20,260 --> 00:33:25,820
And thanks for always being my strength.

286
00:33:25,820 --> 00:33:29,430
Today, I'm formally proposing to you.

287
00:33:29,430 --> 00:33:32,550
Let's date, Teach.

288
00:33:41,530 --> 00:33:45,930
Joon Woo, are you worried about something?

289
00:33:46,840 --> 00:33:48,680
- Oh Je.
- Yeah.

290
00:33:48,680 --> 00:33:54,290
To be honest, I'm thinking about whether
I should go down to be with my mom or not.

291
00:33:54,290 --> 00:33:57,250
Did something happen to her?

292
00:33:58,330 --> 00:34:02,080
I think I should be with her.

293
00:34:02,080 --> 00:34:07,200
Honestly...
she's going through a rough time.

294
00:34:07,970 --> 00:34:10,690
But she only has me,

295
00:34:10,690 --> 00:34:16,180
so I'm going to think about ways to lessen her burden.

296
00:34:17,220 --> 00:34:22,220
- Still...
- When I saw her,

297
00:34:22,220 --> 00:34:25,210
I had a sudden thought.

298
00:34:25,210 --> 00:34:32,170
All this time,
I thought I was lonely because I was alone.

299
00:34:36,210 --> 00:34:41,500
But honestly, isn't my mom who's the loneliest right now?

300
00:34:44,120 --> 00:34:51,860
I now have Soo Bin and you, too.

301
00:34:51,860 --> 00:34:55,120
And I have Teach Han Gyeol.

302
00:34:55,120 --> 00:34:58,520
You're worried about Soo Bin?

303
00:35:17,040 --> 00:35:19,200
Mom, I'm going to the academy.

304
00:35:19,200 --> 00:35:23,840
- Let's work hard since it's the break.
- I got it.

305
00:35:30,940 --> 00:35:33,460
Yes?

306
00:35:36,820 --> 00:35:39,290
Okay.

307
00:35:47,470 --> 00:35:51,740
Hello, thank you making the time.

308
00:35:53,770 --> 00:35:56,700
What is it?

309
00:35:58,020 --> 00:36:00,880
I heard your grades went up a lot.

310
00:36:00,880 --> 00:36:04,210
I've also settled on a career path.

311
00:36:04,210 --> 00:36:09,450
I'm going to go to an art college.
I'm attending an art academy, too.

312
00:36:09,450 --> 00:36:14,160
- Art? I see. It must be hard.
- I'm fine.

313
00:36:14,980 --> 00:36:17,710
What is it you wanted to say?

314
00:36:17,710 --> 00:36:21,880
If you're asking me if you can date Soo Bin then

315
00:36:21,900 --> 00:36:24,980
it's a little hard to answer. Please understand.

316
00:36:24,980 --> 00:36:27,700
It's not about that.

317
00:36:27,700 --> 00:36:34,490
But... I do have a request, so I called.

318
00:36:34,490 --> 00:36:36,940
What kind of request?

319
00:36:38,220 --> 00:36:43,520
With Soo Bin...
I want to see her for just one day.

320
00:36:43,520 --> 00:36:46,910
You should have seen her without telling me.

321
00:36:47,780 --> 00:36:51,000
So that she can feel at ease,

322
00:36:51,000 --> 00:36:56,690
please tell her directly that you'll allow it.

323
00:36:56,690 --> 00:37:01,630
I... think I'm going to go down and...

324
00:37:03,030 --> 00:37:05,930
be with my mom.

325
00:37:10,310 --> 00:37:13,210
So I think we have to be apart for a bit.

326
00:37:14,130 --> 00:37:18,840
Why suddenly? What happened?

327
00:37:18,840 --> 00:37:23,590
Something came up... but

328
00:37:24,880 --> 00:37:28,750
I want to tell Soo Bin myself.

329
00:37:28,750 --> 00:37:36,490
So until then, please keep it a secret.
I ask you.

330
00:37:39,900 --> 00:37:44,420
Okay. Yeah, I got it.

331
00:37:44,420 --> 00:37:47,050
Thank you.

332
00:37:47,850 --> 00:37:50,740
Joon Woo.

333
00:37:52,620 --> 00:37:57,990
Thank you for comforting my Soo Bin before.

334
00:37:57,990 --> 00:38:02,780
Also, I was too emotional about how I dealt with it.

335
00:38:02,780 --> 00:38:05,310
I'm sorry about that.

336
00:38:06,730 --> 00:38:09,570
It's okay.

337
00:38:12,590 --> 00:38:17,620
- I'll leave first then.
- Okay.

338
00:38:32,000 --> 00:38:35,060
- Hello?
- Where are you?

339
00:38:35,060 --> 00:38:40,080
I'm at the academy.
Are you on your way home?

340
00:38:42,110 --> 00:38:45,820
- Yeah.
- What's wrong?

341
00:38:45,820 --> 00:38:50,540
Just...
I feel like we haven't been able to see each other much.

342
00:38:50,540 --> 00:38:55,630
And since we're on vacation, we don't go to school.

343
00:38:56,670 --> 00:38:58,900
Hurry up and go home.

344
00:38:58,900 --> 00:39:02,480
Joon Woo, it's tiring, right?

345
00:39:02,480 --> 00:39:06,990
Still, until the day we can get permission
from my mom and date comfortably,

346
00:39:06,990 --> 00:39:09,320
let's bear with it a little longer.

347
00:39:09,320 --> 00:39:14,360
To be honest, it's okay for me anyway.

348
00:39:14,360 --> 00:39:17,090
Should we meet up now?

349
00:39:17,090 --> 00:39:23,680
No. Until that day.
Hurry up and go home.

350
00:39:23,680 --> 00:39:28,800
- Okay. Bye.
- Bye.

351
00:39:32,560 --> 00:39:36,890
- I'm home.
- You worked hard?

352
00:39:36,890 --> 00:39:43,540
- Were you out?
- Huh? Nearby.

353
00:39:43,540 --> 00:39:48,200
Hey. You...

354
00:39:49,710 --> 00:39:53,230
Since it's your break, meet up if you want.

355
00:39:53,230 --> 00:39:56,270
Who?

356
00:39:56,270 --> 00:39:58,820
Choi Joon Woo.

357
00:39:59,780 --> 00:40:01,720
Why suddenly?

358
00:40:01,720 --> 00:40:05,960
Well, you said to trust you.

359
00:40:05,960 --> 00:40:09,380
And your grades went up,
and you said he's working hard, too.

360
00:40:09,380 --> 00:40:13,910
Not to date but just see each
other for a day and get some air.

361
00:40:17,050 --> 00:40:20,920
Thank you, Mom. It's nice to be able to comfortably
go out even for a day with your permission.

362
00:40:20,920 --> 00:40:23,510
You're not overly happy or anything?

363
00:40:23,510 --> 00:40:26,590
I'm happy. Thank you.

364
00:40:26,590 --> 00:40:32,540
- Joon Woo, the thing you asked me for earlier.
- Thank you.

365
00:40:32,540 --> 00:40:36,410
- It's someone who does private classes near there, so give them a call.
- Yes.

366
00:40:36,410 --> 00:40:40,030
It would be great if you got a prize this time.

367
00:40:41,060 --> 00:40:44,780
I don't think I will. Everyone was so good.

368
00:40:45,520 --> 00:40:49,410
Joon Woo. Choi Joon Woo.

369
00:40:49,410 --> 00:40:54,380
Right now,
I'll make a proposal you could never refuse.

370
00:40:54,380 --> 00:40:59,110
Joon Woo, do you want to go on a date with me today?
All day?

371
00:40:59,110 --> 00:41:02,980
- Mom gave me permission.
- Okay.

372
00:41:02,980 --> 00:41:06,720
Oh, you're at the academy right now, right?
Concentrate. Concentrate.

373
00:41:06,720 --> 00:41:09,170
I'll call you later.

374
00:41:10,240 --> 00:41:15,260
Okay.
Thanks. I'll call you.

375
00:41:38,200 --> 00:41:40,990
You're good.
As expected.

376
00:41:48,160 --> 00:41:50,390
He's quitting.

377
00:42:01,250 --> 00:42:02,950
Joon Woo!

378
00:42:05,450 --> 00:42:09,030
Joon Woo,
I hear you're very talented.

379
00:42:09,030 --> 00:42:13,840
See?
I have a good eye for people.

380
00:42:13,840 --> 00:42:17,070
But why?

381
00:42:17,070 --> 00:42:20,560
I heard you're quitting the academy.

382
00:42:25,670 --> 00:42:27,360
Yes.

383
00:42:30,700 --> 00:42:34,780
I was already thinking that I should tell you first.

384
00:42:36,010 --> 00:42:40,820
I... think I have to be with my mom.

385
00:42:42,710 --> 00:42:44,830
What do you mean?

386
00:42:47,520 --> 00:42:50,970
Are you saying you're going to transfer?

387
00:42:51,720 --> 00:42:55,220
Something difficult happened to my mom,

388
00:42:56,400 --> 00:43:00,760
so I think I have to help her
as much as possible while being with her.

389
00:43:05,300 --> 00:43:09,650
You know, Joon Woo, don't take this the wrong way.

390
00:43:09,650 --> 00:43:12,120
Do you want me to help you a bit?

391
00:43:20,210 --> 00:43:21,790
Teach...

392
00:43:23,580 --> 00:43:28,390
thank you for caring to that extent.

393
00:43:35,220 --> 00:43:40,200
But... you've finally adjusted,

394
00:43:40,200 --> 00:43:44,730
and you've picked your career path
and are going to a good academy.

395
00:43:44,730 --> 00:43:48,050
I think everything's fallen into place.

396
00:43:50,310 --> 00:43:52,430
That's why I'm leaving.

397
00:43:55,120 --> 00:44:00,110
Now, no matter where I am, I have the confidence.

398
00:44:04,120 --> 00:44:06,790
Hey, doing this makes you a runner!

399
00:44:07,500 --> 00:44:11,000
Go and run away! It doesn't make you cool at all!

400
00:44:13,730 --> 00:44:17,790
Choi Joon Woo!
You're a runner!

401
00:44:26,900 --> 00:44:28,910
Okay, Joon Woo.

402
00:44:31,710 --> 00:44:33,620
Go.

403
00:44:35,060 --> 00:44:40,220
Go and take care of your mom.

404
00:44:41,760 --> 00:44:44,430
I think you can do that now.

405
00:44:46,810 --> 00:44:52,850
Without you here, I'll feel a little empty,

406
00:44:54,880 --> 00:44:57,540
but still, I think you can do that now.

407
00:45:51,750 --> 00:45:56,290
Yoo Soo Bin, you look pretty.

408
00:45:58,790 --> 00:46:00,090
I look okay?

409
00:46:00,090 --> 00:46:02,330
You look really pretty.

410
00:46:05,640 --> 00:46:07,750
I'll be back.

411
00:46:11,060 --> 00:46:15,550
Yoo Soo Bin. Also...

412
00:46:18,710 --> 00:46:23,030
I thought about what you said. A lot.

413
00:46:29,810 --> 00:46:32,560
Thank you so much, my daughter...

414
00:46:34,470 --> 00:46:37,100
For giving me courage.

415
00:46:38,350 --> 00:46:42,540
Soo Bin, I'll try and do that.

416
00:46:43,320 --> 00:46:45,060
Okay?

417
00:46:52,950 --> 00:46:55,040
I love you, Mom.

418
00:46:55,040 --> 00:46:57,340
I love you so much.

419
00:46:57,340 --> 00:46:59,810
I was sorry.

420
00:47:07,940 --> 00:47:11,110
- Hi.
- Hi.

421
00:48:24,870 --> 00:48:27,720
One, two, three.

422
00:48:27,720 --> 00:48:30,900
One more time?
One, two, three.

423
00:49:05,510 --> 00:49:07,430
Yoo Pil Sang.

424
00:49:08,800 --> 00:49:12,300
- You want to try to date?
- What?

425
00:49:13,870 --> 00:49:16,510
I'm only saying it one more time.

426
00:49:16,510 --> 00:49:18,850
Let's date.

427
00:49:25,500 --> 00:49:28,180
Sit down!

428
00:49:28,180 --> 00:49:29,350
Sit down!

429
00:49:29,350 --> 00:49:31,440
What are you doing?

430
00:49:38,030 --> 00:49:39,950
It's nice.

431
00:49:59,080 --> 00:50:00,920
Soo Bin.

432
00:50:02,040 --> 00:50:03,550
Yeah?

433
00:50:05,170 --> 00:50:07,080
I have something to tell you.

434
00:50:07,080 --> 00:50:08,880
I know.

435
00:50:11,800 --> 00:50:15,860
I kept getting a strange feeling,

436
00:50:15,860 --> 00:50:19,220
so I called your mom.

437
00:50:19,220 --> 00:50:25,540
After you went to see your mom,
something kept bothering me.

438
00:50:27,120 --> 00:50:31,920
That you...
keep insisting on going down there,

439
00:50:31,920 --> 00:50:34,150
even though she tried to stop you.

440
00:50:39,120 --> 00:50:41,750
I'm sorry for telling you so late.

441
00:50:44,580 --> 00:50:46,980
Guess what I told her.

442
00:50:53,950 --> 00:50:57,550
Hello, this is Yoo Soo Bin.

443
00:50:57,550 --> 00:51:00,610
Yes, I have been well.

444
00:51:02,330 --> 00:51:06,890
Perhaps, is there something going on with Joon Woo?

445
00:51:06,890 --> 00:51:12,340
Joon Woo doesn't seem that well so
I called because I was worried.

446
00:51:13,710 --> 00:51:16,910
It's okay, please tell me.

447
00:51:16,910 --> 00:51:19,580
No matter how I stop him,

448
00:51:19,580 --> 00:51:23,840
Joon Woo, perhaps it really bothers him,

449
00:51:23,840 --> 00:51:26,520
so he keeps saying he wants to come down
and live with me.

450
00:51:26,520 --> 00:51:30,250
That's why I just agreed with him.

451
00:51:30,250 --> 00:51:32,700
You must be upset.

452
00:51:32,700 --> 00:51:35,680
Right?
What should we do?

453
00:51:36,370 --> 00:51:39,720
I'm really fine though.

454
00:51:39,720 --> 00:51:44,710
I'm sure Joon Woo also thought about it a lot.

455
00:51:44,710 --> 00:51:51,000
No matter where Joon Woo is,
it is important that he feels at peace.

456
00:51:51,000 --> 00:51:55,990
If he studies hard and continues to work hard on arts

457
00:51:55,990 --> 00:51:57,480
then it will be fine.

458
00:51:57,480 --> 00:52:02,130
I can just keep in touch with him.

459
00:52:02,130 --> 00:52:04,460
So don't worry.

460
00:52:11,020 --> 00:52:14,860
You went through a lot.

461
00:52:19,360 --> 00:52:21,770
But, Joon Woo...

462
00:52:23,190 --> 00:52:26,480
even though I told her that...

463
00:52:27,780 --> 00:52:32,010
I... still...

464
00:52:40,650 --> 00:52:48,220
Soo Bin, the truth is that you are the one
I am worried most about.

465
00:52:57,260 --> 00:53:01,980
But just because I am going to go to my mom,

466
00:53:03,720 --> 00:53:06,350
it doesn't mean it's over for us.

467
00:53:10,600 --> 00:53:16,900
Each of us, wherever we are, let's be patient.

468
00:53:23,550 --> 00:53:30,080
From now on,
we should not put on a sad or depressed face.

469
00:53:30,080 --> 00:53:31,870
Promise?

470
00:53:36,910 --> 00:53:38,890
Promise.

471
00:53:42,460 --> 00:53:46,400
You're so nice.
Our Soo Bin.

472
00:53:46,400 --> 00:53:49,360
My Joon Woo is so nice.

473
00:54:07,960 --> 00:54:09,940
Congratulations. At the Min Jok Arts College's art contest, Choi Joon Woo received the silver award. Please check the website for the date and place of the ceremony and show.

474
00:54:09,940 --> 00:54:12,560
Joon Woo, you won silver.

475
00:54:12,560 --> 00:54:15,000
You are a silver awardee?

476
00:54:16,300 --> 00:54:18,820
Hey, congrats!

477
00:54:18,820 --> 00:54:21,410
This is so great!

478
00:54:25,580 --> 00:54:26,900
Soo Bin.

479
00:54:26,900 --> 00:54:29,000
Congrats.

480
00:54:32,500 --> 00:54:34,510
Congrats, Joon Woo.

481
00:54:34,510 --> 00:54:36,860
Thank you Soo Bin.

482
00:54:36,860 --> 00:54:39,000
Thank you.

483
00:54:40,930 --> 00:54:43,660
We're here.

484
00:54:43,660 --> 00:54:46,890
Should we go for another round?

485
00:54:46,890 --> 00:54:49,800
It's our seventh round.

486
00:54:49,800 --> 00:54:51,590
You should go home now.

487
00:54:57,060 --> 00:54:59,230
Take care.

488
00:55:08,260 --> 00:55:10,070
Soo Bin.

489
00:55:18,120 --> 00:55:20,820
I have a favor.

490
00:55:21,690 --> 00:55:23,350
What?

491
00:55:24,900 --> 00:55:26,770
When I leave...

492
00:55:29,410 --> 00:55:32,410
I would like for you not to come.

493
00:55:36,790 --> 00:55:38,390
Why?

494
00:55:41,350 --> 00:55:45,080
I don't want to show you me leaving.

495
00:56:01,680 --> 00:56:04,420
I will come to see you again.

496
00:56:08,500 --> 00:56:12,420
After becoming way more cool.

