00:56:40,630 --> 00:56:44,850
♬ Certain days and nights are recalled ♬

498
00:56:44,850 --> 00:56:47,190
My mom will be there when you arrive.

499
00:56:47,190 --> 00:56:48,180
I leave it in your care.
♬ Certain days and nights are recalled ♬

500
00:56:48,180 --> 00:56:53,180
I leave it in your care.
♬ Certain days and nights are recalled ♬

501
00:56:55,130 --> 00:57:04,740
♬ Now the feelings too, like understanding everything ♬

502
00:57:04,740 --> 00:57:08,460
♬ I can spend my time laughing ♬

503
00:57:09,340 --> 00:57:13,650
Joon Woo is leaving today, right?

504
00:57:13,650 --> 00:57:15,220
Yeah.

505
00:57:16,110 --> 00:57:18,730
Go and say goodbye or something.

506
00:57:18,730 --> 00:57:21,380
I have to do this.
The academy's closed today.

